SELECT interactions.id, chat_messages.message, chat_log.message_id FROM chat_log JOIN interactions ON chat_log.interaction_id = interactions.id JOIN chat_messages ON chat_log.message_id = chat_messages.id ORDER BY interactions.id DESC;

SELECT players.username, chat_messages.message, chat_messages.message_time FROM players JOIN chat_messages ON players.id = chat_messages.sender_id WHERE players.registration_date > '2022-01-01' AND chat_messages.receiver_id = 10;

SELECT interactions.id, players.username, chat_messages.message, chat_messages.message_time FROM interactions JOIN players ON interactions.player_id = players.id JOIN chat_messages ON interactions.id = chat_messages.interaction_id WHERE interactions.interaction_type = 'like' ORDER BY chat_messages.message_time DESC;

SELECT players.username, COUNT(*) AS interactions_count FROM players JOIN interactions ON players.id = interactions.player_id GROUP BY players.username HAVING interactions_count > 5 ORDER BY interactions_count DESC;

SELECT interactions.id, chat_messages.message, players.username FROM interactions LEFT JOIN chat_messages ON interactions.id = chat_messages.interaction_id LEFT JOIN players ON interactions.player_id = players.id WHERE interactions.interaction_time BETWEEN '2022-01-01' AND '2022-12-31';
SELECT players.username, COUNT(*) AS sent_messages_count FROM players JOIN chat_messages ON players.id = chat_messages.sender_id GROUP BY players.username ORDER BY sent_messages_count DESC LIMIT 5;
